WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Unzip's start screen: a drop zone to open a ZIP archive.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
An archive is opened; its contents list in a sortable, filterable file tree.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Files download individually or all at once, entirely on your device.
